content: Good to go with children in autumn

A good place to go out to the suburbs of Seoul. Even if you visit Siheung Gaetgol Ecological Park in all four seasons, it is a place that shows a fairy tale-like scenery. It's a good place to travel with your family, and the parking lot is also a good place to use because the public parking lot is good :) tip: Personally, the sunset is a beautiful place
It is said that the scenery here is very good, have the opportunity to see it.
Siheung Gaetgol Ecological Park Pink Muhly is very pretty in autumn. The reeds are also pretty, and I think autumn is the prettiest among spring, summer, autumn and winter.
It's always a fun place to go.Weekend parking is hard but good
love this place especially during spring time
It's really pretty when it's sunset at Gaetgol Ecological Park!!
